No.2290
Connections: 
Text: Minecraft is a sandbox game, so there's no proper way to play the game.

No.2291
Connections: 
Text: In "Survival", food and shelter are essential, however everything else is optional.

No.2292
Connections: 
Text: Even the bare essentials of food and shelter have countless solutions.

No.2293
Connections: 
Text: This guide will show you some of the more common and straightforward solutions to surviving the first day.

No.2294
