Text: First day[edit | edit source].

No.2295
Connections: 
Text: As your first day begins, you will need to collect wood.

No.2296
Connections: 
Text: Collect at least four trees' worth of wood blocks (left click and hold while looking at the tree to break it).

No.2297
Connections: 
Text: First use this to make a crafting table (place the crafting table to use it).

No.2298
Connections: 
Text: Right click your crafting table to access it.

No.2299
Connections: 
Text: The first tool you craft should be a wooden pickaxe.

No.2300
Connections: 
Text: Dig down until you find stone.

No.2301
Connections: 
Text: Mine it with a pickaxe.

No.2302
Connections: 
Text: Mine at least 20 blocks of cobblestone.

No.2303
Connections: stone:7|pickaxe:8 pickaxe:8|stone:7 
Text: Create a stone axe, stone sword, and stone pickaxe.

No.2304
Connections: furnace:3|iron:12 iron:12|furnace:3 
Text: Now craft a furnace to cook meat for food and smelt any iron you find in your travels.

No.2305
Connections: coal:12|wood:5 wood:5|coal:12 
Text: Save around five blocks of wood in case you haven't found any coal yet, and smelt them to create charcoal.

