Text: Punching wood[edit | edit source].

No.2422
Connections: coal:17|stone:22 stone:22|coal:17 
Text: Look around for a few things in particular, in order of priority: trees, visible stone (and especially coal ore, which looks like stone with black spots on it), animals, and tall grass.

No.2423
Connections: 
Text: As you move around, break any tall grass in your way, and collect any seeds that drop.

No.2424
Connections: 
Text: For that matter, collect any loose item you see, as most of them will eventually be handy.

No.2425
Connections: wood:18|block:21 block:21|wood:18 
Text: Your first priority is to find a small tree, bash through the leaves if needed, and "punch" the wood until each block drops as an item.

No.2426
Connections: 
Text: Don't rapidly click on the block, just hold left-click (or whatever you've set "attack" to) until the block breaks.

No.2427
Connections: 
Text: Don't bother with huge trees at this point, but also don't be upset if you can't reach the top blocks of wood — you can always come back and collect them later.

No.2428
Connections: 
Text: This first tree should give you at least 4 blocks of wood ("logs").

No.2429
